item.title: Aspose.Cells for Python via Java 19.12 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes for Aspose.Cells for Python via Java 19.12. Key Summary Category CELLSPYTHONJAVA-9 File Formats and Conversions - XLS, SpreadsheetML (XLSX, XML), Comma Separated Value (CSV), HTML, OpenDocument Spreadsheet (ODS), PDF, Tab Delimited, Plain Text (TXT) New Feature CELLSPYTHONJAVA-10 Rendering and Printing - Render spreadsheet to vector images (EMF) - Render worksheets to raster images (Multipage TIFF, GIF)
